30
00:02:01,940 --> 00:02:02,520
All right. All right.

31
00:02:02,610 --> 00:02:03,860
What's going on with you two?

32
00:02:04,130 --> 00:02:05,730
My date with Gu Xiao was going well.

33
00:02:05,820 --> 00:02:07,250
Then he started stalking me.

34
00:02:07,340 --> 00:02:08,020
No, it's not like that.

35
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:09,820
I was afraid Gu Xiao might
have an ulterior motive

36
