and take advantage of Gao Zhi Yi.

37
00:02:10,750 --> 00:02:11,580
So, I came here.

38
00:02:11,670 --> 00:02:12,770
Me? Taken advantage of?

39
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,510
I think you're the one taking
advantage of me.

40
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,350
Gao Zhi Yi.

41
00:02:15,430 --> 00:02:16,310
All I did was ruin your wish

42
00:02:16,400 --> 00:02:17,240
of sleeping with him.

43
00:02:17,330 --> 00:02:18,410
Sleeping with him?

44
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:19,570
Yi Yi.

45
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,140
You're a girl, after all.

46
00:02:21,229 --> 00:02:23,080
You ought to be chaste.

47
00:02:24,350 --> 00:02:25,229
Lin Nuo.

48
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:26,760
You, buzz off

49
00:02:26,850 --> 00:02:27,800
I'll get out.

50
00:02:29,230 --> 00:02:30,280
Well, Yi Yi.

51
00:02:30,370 --> 00:02:31,820
Just go back.

52
00:02:32,600 --> 00:02:33,070
Why?

53
