55
00:02:36,130 --> 00:02:37,390
Wow, you'll work with injuries!

56
00:02:37,950 --> 00:02:39,670
When did you become so working-hard?

57
00:02:40,250 --> 00:02:40,990
Mr Zhang

58
00:02:41,070 --> 00:02:42,290
recommended me.

59
00:02:42,380 --> 00:02:43,280
I need to be serious about it,

60
00:02:43,370 --> 00:02:44,800
so that I won't disgrace him.

61
00:02:45,850 --> 00:02:46,640
Alright.

62
00:02:46,730 --> 00:02:48,180
The power of love is great.

63
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:49,460
It can transform a person.

64
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:49,930
Alright.

65
00:02:50,020 --> 00:02:51,640
Lin Nuo, you can also
accompany Yi Yi to the outside.

66
00:02:51,730 --> 00:02:52,700
No, thanks.

67
00:02:54,170 --> 00:02:54,820
Bye.

68
00:02:54,910 --> 00:02:55,800
Look!

69
00:02:55,890 --> 00:02:56,770
Go!

70
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:19,520
What?

71
00:03:19,610 --> 00:03:21,440
Why don't you go first?

72
00:03:22,230 --> 00:03:23,270
