76
00:03:28,230 --> 00:03:29,110
I...

77
00:03:29,270 --> 00:03:30,990
Last time I followed you
on your date with Gu Xiao.

78
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:32,240
It's my fault.

79
00:03:32,530 --> 00:03:34,190
But I'm really worried about you.

80
00:03:37,350 --> 00:03:38,230
Lin Nuo,

81
00:03:38,559 --> 00:03:40,160
I know you did it for my sake.

82
00:03:40,890 --> 00:03:41,840
But do you know?

83
00:03:41,920 --> 00:03:43,220
I feel burdened

84
00:03:43,309 --> 00:03:44,390
when you're too nice to me.

85
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,150
But I just want you to live a good life.

86
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,030
Because I know you too well.

87
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,110
When you fall in love with someone,

88
00:03:49,190 --> 00:03:50,550
you will

89
00:03:50,640 --> 00:03:52,260
do so much for him.

90
00:03:52,350 --> 00:03:53,230
I know you've treated me well.

91
00:03:53,630 --> 00:03:55,780
But Gu Xiao is really good to me.

92
00:03:59,050 --> 00:04:00,270
Do you remember?

93
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,840
Three years ago,

94
00:04:01,930 --> 00:04:03,680
I said I wanted to go to Jay's concert.

95
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:04,990
But you said,

96
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:06,620
