97
00:04:06,820 --> 00:04:08,040
It's total chaos.

98
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,690
Noisy, crowded and stuffy.

99
00:04:09,770 --> 00:04:11,120
It's good to be home watching TV.

100
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,310
But two days earlier,

101
00:04:13,860 --> 00:04:16,010
I casually mentioned it to Gu Xiao.

102
00:04:16,200 --> 00:04:17,390
For my sake,

103
00:04:17,470 --> 00:04:20,160
