overnight and got a VIP ticket.

104
00:04:20,370 --> 00:04:21,250
Lin Nuo.

105
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,930
You don't know Gu Xiao.

106
00:04:23,020 --> 00:04:24,140
You shouldn't judge

107
00:04:24,230 --> 00:04:25,350
