happy for no purpose.

115
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,650
Just like I also hope.

116
00:04:42,740 --> 00:04:44,180
Yun Shu would be happy as well.

117
00:04:51,430 --> 00:04:52,309
Thanks.

118
00:05:31,850 --> 00:05:32,740
