213
00:10:08,540 --> 00:10:10,460
You even look good in your ID photo.

214
00:10:10,990 --> 00:10:12,610
Even my ID photo

215
00:10:12,700 --> 00:10:13,780
is very ugly.

216
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,010
Why did you touch my picture?

217
00:10:16,270 --> 00:10:17,150
I didn't touch it.

218
00:10:17,630 --> 00:10:19,040
Mei asked me to give it to you.

219
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:20,380
By the way,

220
00:10:20,470 --> 00:10:21,740
do you still have your ID?

221
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:23,100
Can I have two copies, please?

222
00:10:23,240 --> 00:10:24,240
I have a necklace

223
00:10:24,330 --> 00:10:24,900
that holds pictures.

224
00:10:24,990 --> 00:10:26,770
Have you finished your work yet?

225
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,760
I've done my job.

226
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:33,880
Please check.

227
00:10:39,900 --> 00:10:40,300
How do you feel?

228
00:10:40,390 --> 00:10:41,660
Did you do all this by yourself?

229
00:10:41,750 --> 00:10:42,680
You told me to.

230
00:10:42,770 --> 00:10:44,420
How can I hand it to anyone?

231
00:10:44,510 --> 00:10:45,390
Not bad.

232
00:10:46,050 --> 00:10:46,850
Keep trying.

233
00:10:46,940 --> 00:10:48,810
"Not bad?"

234
00:10:48,890 --> 00:10:50,390
Coming from the mouth

235
00:10:50,480 --> 00:10:51,370
of someone beautiful,

236
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:52,950
these words more satisfying
than getting 100 points.

237
00:10:53,900 --> 00:10:54,970
Don't be smooth-talking.

238
00:10:58,120 --> 00:11:00,410
I've been trying so hard.

239
00:11:01,270 --> 00:11:03,020
Can you promise me

240
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:04,250
one little thing?

241
00:11:04,340 --> 00:11:05,430
Go ahead, if it's official.

242
00:11:05,970 --> 00:11:07,130
No more personal matters.

243
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:11,040
It's the key moment to experience life.

244
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:12,920
Come on.

245
00:11:14,060 --> 00:11:15,790
Are you sure you don't
want to see it again?

246
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,280
Your writers have no experience.

247
00:11:17,370 --> 00:11:18,030
It's a waste of time.

248
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,000
Go ahead.

249
00:11:22,950 --> 00:11:23,570
OK

250
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:24,530
Witnesses.

251
00:11:25,160 --> 00:11:26,430
I'm asking you a question now.

252
00:11:27,810 --> 00:11:29,800
You said you were home
at the time of the murder.

253
00:11:29,890 --> 00:11:31,070
And you know nothing at all.

254
00:11:31,310 --> 00:11:31,970
Right?

255
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:32,940
Yes.

256
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,790
I was watching TV.

257
00:11:34,910 --> 00:11:36,390
Actually, I didn't hear
anything next door.

258
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:38,450
Think carefully.

259
00:11:39,090 --> 00:11:40,850
Everything you say right now

260
00:11:41,440 --> 00:11:43,120
has legal implications.

261
00:11:43,410 --> 00:11:44,290
I know.

262
00:11:44,830 --> 00:11:46,720
Everything I said is true.

263
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:49,160
Then I'll ask you.

264
00:11:49,250 --> 00:11:50,060
What' the program on TV

265
00:11:50,150 --> 00:11:51,720
at that time?

266
00:11:52,350 --> 00:11:54,490
A French movie.

267
00:11:54,570 --> 00:11:55,930
-Meet in Paris-

268
00:11:56,650 --> 00:11:58,810
According to the network
company's report on that day.

269
00:11:58,980 --> 00:12:01,270
There's a wiring problem
in your community.

270
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:02,830
The whole community is offline.

271
00:12:02,920 --> 00:12:03,990
Under such circumstances,

272
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,520
